# Markdown

Follow [docs/style-guide--markdown.md](docs/style-guide--markdown.md). Lint config: [.markdownlint.json](.markdownlint.json).

Pipe tables: leading `|` only (no trailing `|`); **no trailing whitespace** after the last cell on a row.

